data.description: **ASSUMABLE LOAN at 4.5%** Discover your dream home! This stunning two-story gem boasts FOUR SPACIOUS BEDROOMS, with THREE of them having their own BATHROOMS!!! Step into a modern oasis with granite countertops throughout, a soothing grey warm color palette, and exquisite double sink vanity in the master bedroom, complete with a sumptuous tub and elegant walk-in shower. The exterior showcases cultured stone accents in the front and a pristine turf landscaped backyard for your outdoor pleasures. The heart of the home is the kitchen, featuring a granite-topped island and bar, stainless steel appliances, and a captivating, cultured stone backsplash. Don't miss your chance to call this home sweet home! VA buyers have the potential to assume a 4.5% interest rate!
